Setup Bower and Grunt:
  npm install -S grunt grunt-contrib-uglify grunt-bower-concat

Create Gruntfile:
  Gruntfile.js

Setup Bower:
  bower init

Write Gruntfile contents (see Gruntfile)

Run Grunt to make sure there are no errors:
  grunt

Install jQuery and Backbone:
  bower install -S jquery backbone

Run Grunt again to execute Gruntfile:
  grunt

Create index page, with concatenated Grunt file in place of vendor files.

Install Handlebars as a Bower component:
  bower install -S handlebars

Run Grunt again to execute Gruntfile:
  grunt
